notes:
EnvelopedData should be used instead of the deprecated EncryptedValue, through the introduction of the EncryptedKey (https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc9810#section-5.3.19.9).
   EncryptedKey ::= CHOICE {
      encryptedValue        EncryptedValue, -- deprecated
      envelopedData     [0] EnvelopedData }
